NK039(ti)006:1: // ma mo'i spyi bskang rin chen spungs pa bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)006:3: mchog chen bsgral ba'i dus sam /
NK039(ti)006:4: ma mo'i mtshan ltas ngan pa'i dus sam /
NK039(ti)006:5: las mi dge ba 'byung ba'i dus sam /
NK039(ti)006:8: drag po'i las la sbyar ba'i dus su /
NK039(ti)006:9: sngon du bskang bshags kyi cho ga 'di bya'o //
NK039(ti)006:10: 'di ni las thams cad gang la gces /
NK039(ti)006:11: rnal 'byor sgrub pa la brtson pa rnams kyi shin tu brtson par bya'o //
NK039(ti)006:12: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi bskang bshags kyi cho ga rdzogs pa yod /
NK039(ti)006:14: dur khrod chen po'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)006:15: bcom ldan dpal chen che mchog he ru ka /
NK039(ti)006:16: mthing nag 'bar ba 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK039(ti)006:17: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK039(ti)006:18: spyan dgu phyag drug zhal bzhi bsgrad //
NK039(ti)006:19: sma ra smin ma dbu skra gyen 'brar khams //
NK039(ti)006:20: glang chen zhing stag thod sbrul brgyan //
NK039(ti)006:21: khrag zhag thal ba'i mtshan mas btab //
NK039(ti)006:22: thugs rjes dbyings las rol par mdzad //
NK039(ti)006:23: gtso mchog 'bar ba'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:24: gtso mchog 'bar ba'i thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:25: lcang lor bcas pa'i pad+ma b+han d+ha la //
NK039(ti)006:26: tshe 'dzin mchog gi mar me dam pas skang //
NK039(ti)006:27: pad+ma zil tig dri dang rak+ta khrag /
NK039(ti)006:28: rdo rje las kyi chu dang pan tsa a mrir ta //
NK039(ti)006:29: sha chen mkha' lding shel sgong gzugs kyis skong //
NK039(ti)006:30: sman chen lnga dang tshe 'dzin byi ma der //
NK039(ti)006:31: sbyor dang sgrol ba'i bdud rtsi mchog nyid 'dis //
NK039(ti)006:32: dpal chen 'bar ba'i thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:33: thugs dam bskang ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK039(ti)006:34: rnal 'byor bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)006:35: srid pa'i ma mo dbang du bsdus //
NK039(ti)006:36: dmigs pa'i dgra bo myur du sgrol //
NK039(ti)006:37: 'di nas mar yum chen mo 'dod pa'i dbang mo
NK039(ti)006:38: che mu kha le la sogs pa'i dbyings kyi yum
NK039(ti)006:41: gtso mo yum gyi mngon spyod ma //
NK039(ti)006:42: spyi gtsug g.yu yi rdo rje rtse dgu 'bar //
NK039(ti)006:43: g.yu'i ral pa khams gsum khyabs //
NK039(ti)006:44: g.yas kyi phyag na rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:45: g.yon gyi phyag na bdud rtsi longs spyod 'byed //
NK039(ti)006:46: ye shes rol pa'i spyan gyis kun du gzigs //
NK039(ti)006:47: khams gsum srid gsum kun la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:48: gtso mo yum chen thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:50: chos kyi dbyings phyug chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:51: nam mkha' rigs kyi bdag mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:52: mkha' 'gro chen mo rdo rje'i gdong //
NK039(ti)006:53: rtag pa'i rgyal mo bkrag gsal mnyam //
NK039(ti)006:54: na bza' ser po gtso ma gsol //
NK039(ti)006:55: phyag na rgyal mtshan spu gri bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:56: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)006:57: 'gro ba'i bkrag la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:58: mkha' 'gro bkrag gsal thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:60: rdo rje dbyings phyug chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:61: shar phyogs khams kyi mnga' bdag ste //
NK039(ti)006:62: mkha' 'gro chen mo seng ge'i gdong //
NK039(ti)006:63: rtag pa'i rgyal mo rnam snang gsal //
NK039(ti)006:64: na bza' dkar mo shel ltar gsal //
NK039(ti)006:65: phyag na dgra sta gtun shing bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:66: 'byung ba sa la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)006:67: 'gro ba'i sha la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:68: mkha' 'gro rnam snang thugs dam skang //
NK039(ti)006:70: rin chen dbyings phyug chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:71: lho phyogs khams kyi mnga' bdag ste //
NK039(ti)006:72: mkha' 'gro chen mo ban glang gdong //
NK039(ti)006:75: phyag na me dpung dbyug to bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:76: 'byung ba me la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)006:77: 'gro ba'i drod la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:80: pad+ma dbyings phyug chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:81: nub phyogs khams kyi mnga' bdag ste //
NK039(ti)006:82: mkha' 'gro chen mo kang ka'i gdong //
NK039(ti)006:83: rtag pa'i rgyal mo gnyen gsal ma //
NK039(ti)006:84: na bza' dmar po dbang gi mdzes //
NK039(ti)006:85: phyag na zhags pa tri shu la //
NK039(ti)006:86: 'byung ba chu la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)006:87: 'gro ba'i khrag la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:88: mkha' 'gro gnyen gsal thugs dam skang //
NK039(ti)006:90: las kyi dbyings phyug chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:91: byang phyogs khams kyi mnga' bdag ste //
NK039(ti)006:92: mkha' 'gro chen mo khyung chen gdong //
NK039(ti)006:93: rtag pa'i rgyal mo yang gsal g.yos //
NK039(ti)006:94: nab bza' ljang gu shin tu 'bar //
NK039(ti)006:96: 'byung ba rlung la dbang 'gro ba'i dbugs la mnga' mkha' 'gro yang gsal thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:97: gtso mo yum chen la sogs te //
NK039(ti)006:98: dbyings kyi yum drug thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:99: mkha' lding nag po zangs mchu dang //
NK039(ti)006:100: tsa ra rog po mkhal dkar dang //
NK039(ti)006:101: shel sgong nag po spyi dkar dang //
NK039(ti)006:102: mkha' lding nag mo gser mig dang //
NK039(ti)006:104: sha chen tshil chen a mri ta //
NK039(ti)006:105: dam rdzas rmad byung gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)006:106: bdud rtsi rnam lngar sbyar ba 'dis //
NK039(ti)006:107: dbyings kyi yum drug thugs dam skong gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:109: mchod do ma srin rgya mtsho mchod //
NK039(ti)006:110: bskang ngo bskal par thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:111: dam tshig nyams ni ma nyam na //
NK039(ti)006:112: nyams na bdud rtsi sman gyi bskang //
NK039(ti)006:113: lta ba log ni ma log na //
NK039(ti)006:114: log na chos nyid dbyings la lta //
NK039(ti)006:115: ma mo g.yel ni ma g.yel na //
NK039(ti)006:116: ma mo g.yel na rdzas kyii bsten //
NK039(ti)006:118: 'khrul na nongs pa rjes su bshags //
NK039(ti)006:119: bskang gso rgyan chen lha la 'bul /
NK039(ti)006:120: mthun pa'i rdzas chen ngas 'bul gyis //
NK039(ti)006:121: nga yi las bcol grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)006:122: thugs dam bskang ba'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK039(ti)006:124: mi la na tsha ma btang la //
NK039(ti)006:125: phyag la god 'gram ma shor cig /
NK039(ti)006:126: zhing la btsa' sad ser gsum snam ma 'dren //
NK039(ti)006:127: dam tshig nyams chag bskangs bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)006:128: chags chen nyams pa bzlog tu gsol //
NK039(ti)006:129: bdud kyi zhags pa nag po chod //
NK039(ti)006:130: gshin rje'i khram kha dgra la bsgyur //
NK039(ti)006:131: rnal 'byor sku tshe bsring ba dang //
NK039(ti)006:132: dgra bo dam nyams brlag ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)006:133: sgrub mchog bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)006:134: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyung cig /
NK039(ti)006:135: thugs dam gnyen po bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:137: srid pa bde 'gro khams gsum yul mchog ma //
NK039(ti)006:138: sku mdog mthing nag chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:139: dbu dang zhabs kyi stong khams khyab //
NK039(ti)006:140: rin chen ral pas snang srid kheb //
NK039(ti)006:141: phyag na g.yang bzhi ba dan bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:142: khyod ni 'dod khams gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:143: phud kyi bdag mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:145: dpag bsam shing gi yal ga la //
NK039(ti)006:146: dkar mo g.yag thod ral gcig ma //
NK039(ti)006:147: nyi zla stong gi thod phreng can //
NK039(ti)006:148: phyag na zangs kyi dril zhig bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:149: snang srid snying gi bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:150: nyi zla thod phreng thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:152: rdo rje nyi ma khrag 'thung 'khros pa'i dbang mo che //
NK039(ti)006:153: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)006:154: phyag na zangs kyi dril zhag 'bar ba bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:155: khams gsum thams cad gsal mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:156: che zhe chen mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:158: rin chen khrag 'thung 'khros pa'i dbang mo che //
NK039(ti)006:159: sku mdog ser nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)006:160: phyag na dar nag 'khor lo bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:161: khams gsum thams cad dbang du bsdud //
NK039(ti)006:162: che zhe chen mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:164: pad ma srid gsum khrag 'thung 'khros pa'i dbang mo che //
NK039(ti)006:165: sku mdog dmar nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)006:166: phyag na lcags gtun ral gri bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:167: khams gsum thams cad bde la sbyor //
NK039(ti)006:168: che zhe chen mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:170: las kyi stong gsum khrag 'thung khros pa'i dbang mo che //
NK039(ti)006:171: sku mdog ljang nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)006:172: phyag na gsal shing lcags kyu bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:173: khams gsum thams cad gsal bar sbyor //
NK039(ti)006:174: che zhe chen mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:176: mtshan ni dbyings phyug chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:177: sku mdog dkar mo seng ge'i g+ho //
NK039(ti)006:178: lag na mi'i thod pa thog /
NK039(ti)006:179: ma mo khrag 'thung thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:181: mtshan ni srid pa'i rgyan byed ma //
NK039(ti)006:182: sku mdog ser mo stag lpags gyon //
NK039(ti)006:183: lag na skra'i zhags pa bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:184: ma mo sha zan thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:186: mtshan ni bdag nyid chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:187: sku mdog nag mo chu srin gyon //
NK039(ti)006:188: lag na zhing gi dbyug pa thog /
NK039(ti)006:189: ma mo me 'bar thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:191: mtshan ni gcig pu chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:192: sku mdog ljang nag shing lpags gyon //
NK039(ti)006:193: lag na zhing gi g.yang gzhi thog /
NK039(ti)006:194: ma mo rtsis 'debs thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:196: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)006:197: srid pa shar gyi bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:198: dkar mo chen mo spyan gcig ma //
NK039(ti)006:200: dkar mo'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:202: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)006:203: srid pa lha mo'i bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:204: nag mo chen mo che ba can //
NK039(ti)006:206: nag mo'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:208: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)006:209: srid pa nub kyi bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:210: dmar mo chen mo dbang bsgyur ma //
NK039(ti)006:212: dmar mo'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:214: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)006:215: srid pa byang gi bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:216: ser mo chen mo las mkhan ma //
NK039(ti)006:218: ser mo'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:219: srid pa bde 'gro la sogs te //
NK039(ti)006:220: ye shes ma mo bcu bzhi'i thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:221: mkha' lding nag mo zangs chu dang //
NK039(ti)006:222: tsa ra rog po mkhal dkar dang //
NK039(ti)006:223: shel sgong nag mo spyi dkar dang //
NK039(ti)006:224: mkha' lding nag mo gser mig dang //
NK039(ti)006:226: sha chen tshil chen a mri ta //
NK039(ti)006:227: dam rdzas rmad byung gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)006:228: bdud rtsi rnam lnga sbyar ba 'dis //
NK039(ti)006:229: ye shes ma mo bcu bzhi'i thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:233: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo che //
NK039(ti)006:234: sku mdog mthing nag chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:235: phra men bcu drug dbu la rdzogs //
NK039(ti)006:236: rma bya'i sgros ni rgyan du byas //
NK039(ti)006:238: phyag g.yon ne'u le rin chen mdzod //
NK039(ti)006:239: chibs su bong bu dmar gwa bcib //
NK039(ti)006:240: nag mo chen mo'i thugs de'i g.yog mo kha khrid ni /
NK039(ti)006:241: srin mo ma d+ha phur pa'i lha //
NK039(ti)006:242: klu mo gzhog skem chu srin mgo //
NK039(ti)006:243: sku mdog dmar nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)006:244: lag na kha tam rtse gsum thog /
NK039(ti)006:245: khol mo nag mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:247: ma chen thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK039(ti)006:248: dpal ldan gnyen gyi re ma ti //
NK039(ti)006:249: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK039(ti)006:250: zhing lpag re lde nag po gsol //
NK039(ti)006:251: phyag na khram shing sho d+hil bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:252: chibs su drel rta rkang gsum bcib //
NK039(ti)006:253: re ma ti'i thugs dam g.yon gnyis mdzes pa'i tshul gyi rol //
NK039(ti)006:254: ba lam chen mo drel sna ma //
NK039(ti)006:255: phyag na g.yab dar nag po thog /
NK039(ti)006:256: chibs su bong nag kha 'ar bcibs //
NK039(ti)006:257: ba lam nag mo'i thugs dam khris sman nag mo ldem drug ma //
NK039(ti)006:258: phyag na mi mgo thod dbyug thog /
NK039(ti)006:259: chibs su chu bya rog mo bcib //
NK039(ti)006:260: khri sman si li'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:262: sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK039(ti)006:263: phyag brnyan nag mo 'bum gyi bskor //
NK039(ti)006:264: sku'i sprul pa chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:265: dpal ldan nag mo re ma dza //
NK039(ti)006:266: sku la re lde nag mo gsol //
NK039(ti)006:267: phyag na gshin rje khram shing bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:268: chibs su drel nag rkang gsum bcib //
NK039(ti)006:269: sku'i sprul pa'i thugs gsung gi sprul pa chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:270: dpal ldan lha mo re ma dzi //
NK039(ti)006:271: sku la smug nag 'thib pa gyon //
NK039(ti)006:272: lag na nad kyi rkyal pa bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:273: chibs su chu glung nag po bcib //
NK039(ti)006:274: gsung gi sprul pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:275: thugs kyi sprul pa chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:276: dpal ldan nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)006:277: sku la mi lpags rlon pa gyon //
NK039(ti)006:278: lag na mi go khram bam bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:279: chibs su bswe'i sha ba bcib //
NK039(ti)006:280: thugs kyi sprul pa'i thugs dpyid kyi rgyal mo gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)006:281: dkar mo sha ri dur khrod gnas nyul ma //
NK039(ti)006:282: khrag 'thung chen mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:283: dbyar gyi rgyal mor gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)006:284: ba ka hri sti mkha' la char 'bebs ma //
NK039(ti)006:285: sbyor bdag chen mo'i thugs ston gyis rgyal mor gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)006:286: mthing nag mi srun ral pa can //
NK039(ti)006:287: srog bdag chen mo'i rgun gyi rgyal mor gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)006:288: me za brag gyon rgya mtsho'i gting nyul ma //
NK039(ti)006:289: khri za stong sgrol thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:290: lha mo bcu bzhis thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:291: mkha' lding nag mo zangs tsa ra rog po mkhal
NK039(ti)006:292: shel sgong nag po spyi mkhal lding nag mo gser
NK039(ti)006:293: khrag gi 'od zer sha chen tshil dam rdzas rmad
NK039(ti)006:294: bdud rtsi rnam lngar sbyar ba 'dis //
NK039(ti)006:295: lha mo bcu bzhis thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:298: srin mo chen mo sham sham mo //
NK039(ti)006:299: gos su mi lpags rlon pa gyon //
NK039(ti)006:300: srid pa chags byed chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)006:301: phyag na mo g+ho sor 'phreng bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:302: srid pa kun gyi bdag nyid ma //
NK039(ti)006:303: a phyi chen mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:304: khyim bdag chen mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)006:305: stag lpags g.yang gzhi gos su gyon //
NK039(ti)006:306: phyag na rtse gsum 'bar ba bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:307: gsang mtshan he ru ka ni bya //
NK039(ti)006:308: khyod ni 'dod khams gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:309: a phyi chen mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:310: rnal 'byor chen mo srid pa'i bdag /
NK039(ti)006:311: e ka tsa ti ral gcig ma //
NK039(ti)006:312: sku la sprin nag gos su gyon //
NK039(ti)006:313: phyag na kha tam 'bar ba bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:314: gsang mtshan pho nya yongs kyi gtso //
NK039(ti)006:315: ma mo chen mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:316: rin chen sa steg mdzes pa'i mchog /
NK039(ti)006:317: sku la mu stegs gos su mnab //
NK039(ti)006:318: phyag na g.yu'i za ma tog /
NK039(ti)006:319: nam mkha' rgyal mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:320: grub pa'i rnal 'byor mthu mo che //
NK039(ti)006:321: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)006:322: phyag na khram bam shod dril bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:323: gling bzhi spyi phud thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:325: sku la dar dkar g.yu bran mnab //
NK039(ti)006:326: phyag na gser gyi lcags kyu bsnam //
NK039(ti)006:328: rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)006:329: dbu brgya ma la spyan stong ma //
NK039(ti)006:330: 'jig tshul rngams pa'i cha byad can //
NK039(ti)006:331: rdo rje sgeg mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:332: pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)006:333: sa bdag chen po pad ma 'phring //
NK039(ti)006:334: lag na thod pa khrag gi bkang //
NK039(ti)006:335: sa bdag chen mo'i thugs srid pa'i ma mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:336: mkha' lding nag tsa ra shel sgong mkha' lding khrag
NK039(ti)006:337: gi sha chen dam rdzas bdud rtsi srid pa'i ma
NK039(ti)006:338: mo brgyad kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:340: har ting dkar mo chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:341: byang shar mtshams kyi gru 'deg ma //
NK039(ti)006:342: dun ting nag mo chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:343: shar lho mtshams kyi gru 'deg ma //
NK039(ti)006:344: shan ting dmar mo chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:345: lho nub mtshams kyi gru dun ting ser mo chen mo la //
NK039(ti)006:346: nub byang mtshams kyi gru gling bzhi gru 'deg thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:347: shar gyi dkar mo mche ba gtsigs //
NK039(ti)006:348: lho'i nag mo kha rlal ma //
NK039(ti)006:349: nub kyi ma mo mchu 'jib ma //
NK039(ti)006:350: byang gi ser mo skang ldag ma //
NK039(ti)006:351: rig bzhi dmag dpung mang po'i bskor //
NK039(ti)006:352: dmag gi rgyal mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:353: las kyi sring mo chen mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)006:354: gling bzhi mgyog ma lha'i sring mo dang //
NK039(ti)006:355: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK039(ti)006:356: dmar mo g.yag thod klu'i sring nag mo sder 'dzin
NK039(ti)006:357: gnod sbyin las kyi sring bzhi'i thugs 'dod khams ma
NK039(ti)006:358: mo bcu bzhis thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:359: mkha' lding nag mo tsa ra rog po shel sgong
NK039(ti)006:360: nag mkha' lding khrag gi 'od zer sha chen dam
NK039(ti)006:361: rdzas bdud rtsi rnam 'dod khams ma mo bcu bzhis
NK039(ti)006:363: dur khrod gnas pa'i ma mo bdun //
NK039(ti)006:364: rgya mtsho chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)006:365: dpal ldan shugs 'gro'i bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:366: ri rab bsnyil ba'i rngam stabs can //
NK039(ti)006:367: rdo rje kun grags thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:368: khro bo rngam pa'i dkyiil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)006:371: kun tu bzang mo'i thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:373: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)006:374: bdud dpung drag stobs kun 'dus ma //
NK039(ti)006:375: rdo rje kun gsal thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:376: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)006:377: pho nya drug cu'i gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)006:378: sha chen khrag gi longs spyod ma //
NK039(ti)006:379: ye shes mchog gi thugs h'u /
NK039(ti)006:380: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dal la gnas //
NK039(ti)006:381: ma mo gtum chen za byed ma //
NK039(ti)006:382: rdo rje ra ba'i 'phreng thog ma //
NK039(ti)006:385: zhags pa stong gi 'debs ldan ma //
NK039(ti)006:388: dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)006:390: dam tshig nyam pa bsreg mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:391: rdo rje g.yu sgron thugs srid pa'i ma bdun thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:392: mkha' lding nag mo tsa ra rog po shel sgong
NK039(ti)006:393: nag mo mkha' lding khrag gi sha chen tshil dam
NK039(ti)006:394: rdzas rmad bdud rtsi rnam srid pa'i ma bdun 'bul
NK039(ti)006:396: phyi rims 'bar ba'i me dpung las //
NK039(ti)006:397: dbang phyug smug nag nyi shu brgyad //
NK039(ti)006:398: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK039(ti)006:399: tshangs pa dmar ser rin chen 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:400: dbang phyug lha chen tri shu la //
NK039(ti)006:402: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK039(ti)006:403: rgyal byin dkar mo rdo rje gding //
NK039(ti)006:404: ka la nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:405: shar gyi ma bdun thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:406: rdo rje dmar mo thod khrag 'thung //
NK039(ti)006:407: bdud rtsi dmar mo bum pa bsnams //
NK039(ti)006:408: zla ba dkar mo su d+ha ri //
NK039(ti)006:409: be con ljang gu dbyug to phyar //
NK039(ti)006:410: srin mo dmar mo dung chen khrag /
NK039(ti)006:411: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK039(ti)006:412: tsan+d+ha dmar ser ra g+ho zhag /
NK039(ti)006:413: lho'i ma bdun thugs rdo rje dmar mo gter 'chang ma //
NK039(ti)006:414: stobs chen dkar mo b+han d+ha gshol //
NK039(ti)006:415: rdo rje dmar mo spu gris gcod //
NK039(ti)006:417: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:418: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:419: bum pa ka rna lcags sgrog dmar //
NK039(ti)006:420: nub kyi ma bdun thugs gsod ma nag mo ral gri phyar //
NK039(ti)006:421: mi mo dmar mo gsal shing 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:422: phag mo nag mo che zhags 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:423: rgan byed nag mo zhing chung za //
NK039(ti)006:424: sna chen dkar mo thod khrag 'chang //
NK039(ti)006:425: rdo rje chu srin sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK039(ti)006:426: lam po da ra dbyangs bsnyen 'chang //
NK039(ti)006:427: byang gi ma bdun thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:428: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:429: mkha' lding nag po zang tsa ra shel sgong mkha'
NK039(ti)006:430: lding khrag gi 'od zer sha chen dam rdzas bdud
NK039(ti)006:431: rtsi rnam lnga dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad thugs
NK039(ti)006:435: srid gsum sgrol ba'i khas ches ma //
NK039(ti)006:436: gtso chen 'bar ba bdun gyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:437: thog med shugs kyi bsgrod pa'i 'phrul mo che //
NK039(ti)006:438: 'bar ma srin mo bdun gyi thugs ci bgyi bka' nyan las byed ma //
NK039(ti)006:439: pho nya las mkhan bdun gyi gdug rtsub thod dbyug drag po'i 'dul mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:440: srin mo thor rtsug bzhi'i dkyil 'khor phyi rim dbang du bsdud mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)006:441: brtan ma bcu gnyis thugs shugs kyi 'dren pa'i thugs pho nya rgya mtsho ci bgyis bka' nyan tshogs //
NK039(ti)006:442: ma sring rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:443: mkha' lding nag mo zang tsa ra rog po shel
NK039(ti)006:444: sgong mkha' lding khrag gi sha chen dam rdzas bdud
NK039(ti)006:445: rtsi ma sring rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang gyur cig
NK039(ti)006:448: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)006:449: rdo rje ya phyin mthu mo che //
NK039(ti)006:450: rdo rje de phyin rtsal mo che //
NK039(ti)006:451: rdo rje bse phyin dbang mo che //
NK039(ti)006:452: rdo rje phag phyin stobs mo che //
NK039(ti)006:454: ri rab gling bzhi'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)006:455: shar gyi stag srin zor gdong ma //
NK039(ti)006:456: lho'i bam srin dred mong gdong //
NK039(ti)006:457: nub kyi skong srin ban glang gdong //
NK039(ti)006:458: byang gi 'brang srin chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)006:460: thog bdag chen mo bu yug ma //
NK039(ti)006:461: gnam sman bcu gsum thugs sras mo mchog gi tsa mun ti //
NK039(ti)006:462: ma mo spun gsum mkha' 'gro sde bzhi'i dman mo'i
NK039(ti)006:463: tshogs kyi skyong ma chen mo'i brtan ma bcu gnyis
NK039(ti)006:465: ma mo seng ge'i mgo can dang //
NK039(ti)006:466: ma mo stag gi mgo ma mo 'brug gi mgo
NK039(ti)006:467: ma ma bya rgod mgo sprul pa bzhi'i thugs shel
NK039(ti)006:469: gser gyi stag mo mgo lnga pa //
NK039(ti)006:470: ur mo 'brug sngon so snon ma //
NK039(ti)006:471: lcags kyi khyi ste rkang gsum pa //
NK039(ti)006:472: pho nya bzhi'i thugs lcags kyi spyang mo g+ho dgu ma //
NK039(ti)006:473: zangs kyi wa mo rkang brgyad ma //
NK039(ti)006:474: phyogs bcu'i steng gi 'jig rten nas //
NK039(ti)006:475: dpa' bo dang ni dpa' mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)006:476: mkha' 'gro mu mtha' khyab pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)006:477: mu mtha' khyab pa'i thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:478: mkha' lding nag po zang tsa ra rog po shel
NK039(ti)006:479: sgong nag po mkha' lding nag mo khrag gi sha
NK039(ti)006:480: chen dam rdzas bdud rtsi dpa' bo dpa' mo'i tshogs
NK039(ti)006:481: kyi thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:483: sprul pa'i pho nya mgyog ma'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)006:484: seng stag dam dred 'phar spyang dang //
NK039(ti)006:485: lce spyang li 'du wa dang gzigs //
NK039(ti)006:486: stag dang sre mong byi la'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)006:487: rgod khyung kang ka bzhad dang khwa //
NK039(ti)006:488: kyi ling 'ug pa bya rog dang //
NK039(ti)006:489: ne tso khrung khrung bya klag khyi //
NK039(ti)006:490: kha dang sbrul dang ne le dang //
NK039(ti)006:491: sprul pa'i tshogs kyi thugs sprul pa'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)006:492: mkha' lding nag mo zang tsa ra rog po shel
NK039(ti)006:493: sgong nag mo mkha' lding khrag gi 'od zer sha
NK039(ti)006:494: chen dam rdzas rmad bdud rtsi rnam lnga sprul pa'i
NK039(ti)006:495: tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)006:503: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma /
NK039(ti)006:504: dam rdzas tshang ba phyung la /
NK039(ti)006:510: tshil chen mar me sbar dang /
NK039(ti)006:514: ras chen gyi rgyal mtshan dang /
NK039(ti)006:517: thod pa ltag sprad kyi rnga dang /
NK039(ti)006:520: mi rkang gi pho gling mo gling dang /
NK039(ti)006:526: lha bshos khrag gi byug pa dgu /
NK039(ti)006:527: sems can srog dbugs tshang ba /
NK039(ti)006:528: de la sogs pa'i rdzas rnams gsog pa dang /
NK039(ti)006:529: las gzhung so so nas 'byung ba'i thugs dam bskang ba dang /
NK039(ti)006:531: nyams pa che na sems can gsum /
NK039(ti)006:534: nyams pa 'bring na sems can gnyis /
NK039(ti)006:537: nyams pa chung na sbyin sreg brgya /
NK039(ti)006:539: 'dzab brgya yang yig brgya de dang 'dra /
NK039(ti)006:543: srid pa'i ma mo'i rgyud thams cad nas bskang gso rin chen spung pa zhes bya'o //
NK039(ti)006:544: rnal 'byor sgrub pa la brtson pa'i don du mdzad pa /
NK039(ti)006:545: mkha' 'gro ma thams cad kyi bskang gso bsdu legs brten pa rdzogs so //
